\c 10
\s Ukuru hwaModhekai
\p
\v 1 Zvino mambo Ahasuwerusi wakaisa mutero panyika nezviwi zvegungwa\x + Isa. 11.11. 24.15.\x*.
\v 2 Zvino basa rese rekugwinya kwake neresimba rake\x + 9.29.\x*, nedudziro yeukuru hwaModhekai\x + 4.7.\x*, mambo hwaakamukurisa nahwo\x + 8.15. 9.4.\x*, hazvina kunyorwa here mubhuku reMakoronike emadzimambo eMedhiya nePerisiya\x + 2.23. 6.1.\x*?
\v 3 Nokuti Modhekai muJudha wakava wechipiri pana mambo Ahasuwerusi\x + 2 Makor. 28.7. Gen.. 41.40.\x*, uye mukuru pakati peVaJudha, uye achigamuchirwa nechaunga chehama dzake\x + Det. 33.24.\x*, achitsvakira vanhu vake zvakanaka, uye achitaura rugare kumbeu yake yose\x + Neh. 2.10. Map. 122.8,9.\x*.